{"id":24496,"date":"2017-03-10T18:33:04","date_gmt":"2017-03-10T14:33:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=24496"},"modified":"2025-06-25T20:41:45","modified_gmt":"2025-06-25T16:41:45","slug":"prophet-sword-condemns-unjust-war","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/03\/10\/prophet-sword-condemns-unjust-war\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Aggression: The Prophet\u2019s sword condemns unjust killing"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Aisha reported: I found an engraving on the sword of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, that wrote, \u201c<strong>Verily, the worst of people in insolence are those who strike those who never struck anyone, a man who kills those who never killed anyone, and a man who claims allegiance to those other than his rightful benefactors. Whoever does so has disbelieved in Allah and His Messenger. Allah will not accept his obligatory or voluntary deeds<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Bayhaqi\u0304&nbsp;15896<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em>Hasan li ghayrihi<\/em> (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Busiri<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u062c\u064e\u062f\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0645\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0643\u0650\u062a\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064b\u0627 \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0634\u064e\u062f\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u062a\u064f\u0648\u0651\u064b\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u